[{"title":"物理博客开张","url":"/physics-notes-blog/posts/5fd8/","content":"\n这里是我的物理课程学习笔记博客，用来整理物理课程的笔记、推导与错题。\n\n计划覆盖的内容：\n\n- 大学物理（力学、电磁学、热学、光学）\n- 理论力学\n- 其他物理相关课程\n\n公式用 MathJax 渲染：\n\n$$\n\\oint_S \\vec{E} \\cdot d\\vec{S} = \\frac{Q_{enc}}{\\varepsilon_0}\n$$\n\n主博客请访问 [flowwalker.top](https://flowwalker.top)。\n","tags":["开篇"],"categories":["站务"]},{"url":"/physics-notes-blog/index.html"},{"title":"分类","url":"/physics-notes-blog/categories/index.html"},{"title":"标签","url":"/physics-notes-blog/tags/index.html"},{"title":"四处仙山","url":"/physics-notes-blog/links/index.html","content":"\n天涯即比邻。此处为笔者的其他专题仙山之地, 敬请赏玩~\n\n<div class=\"link-card-wrapper\">\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io\" class=\"link-card\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"link-card-title\">flowwalker 的主博客</span>\n    <span class=\"link-card-desc\">每有会意, 便欣然忘食</span>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/math-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <span class=\"link-card-title\">数术Blog</span>\n    <span class=\"link-card-desc\">隔江人在雨声中, 回首向来萧瑟...</span>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/coding-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <span class=\"link-card-title\">码艺Blog</span>\n    <span class=\"link-card-desc\">fingers flutter like butterflies over keys</span>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/engineering-notes-blog/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <span class=\"link-card-title\">工巧Blog</span>\n    <span class=\"link-card-desc\">于浩歌狂热之际饮冰寒凉</span>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://flowwalker.github.io/flowwalker-wiki/\" class=\"link-card\">\n    <span class=\"link-card-title\">flowwalker 的 Wiki</span>\n    <span class=\"link-card-desc\">用 Obsidian + Quartz 编织的知识网络</span>\n  </a>\n</div>\n"},{"title":"关于","url":"/physics-notes-blog/about/index.html","content":"\n这里是记载我物理相关思考的博客。\n\n小县城退役物理奥赛一枚, 曾经国赛Ag; 小学到初中时期都喜欢数学, 但受限于小县城竞赛资源, 不得不面对现实中的压力\n"}]